Package prisonescape.game.model

Class Summary
AlarmSystem This class holds the logic of the game's alarm system.
Dialogue Dialogue parses and formats all data within a given XML document to select the appropriate dialogue to be displayed.
Teleporter Stores the information required to be able to move between rooms within the map.
TeleporterDestination Stores the information about the teleporter source.
TeleporterSource Stores the information about the teleporter destination.
Tile Represents an individual tile of a map for the game.
TiledModel Represents a model of an individual map within the game.
